{"tid":1915300,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香城online攻略 半夜賊人爆門入屋點算好？拳頭在近官府在遠 保命3招必學！","createTime":"2020-03-08T06:21:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T06:29:08.000Z","uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7fe2426423e2b83d669863a8ab22aa2ebc9850a0","tid":1915300,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T06:21:53.000Z","msg":"按照賽局理論，得出下面結果：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cx79t91.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcx79t91.png&h=3fa91347&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n結論係玩家反抗先係王道。<br />\n<br />\n賊人半夜會假冒香城警察爆門入屋，身為東道主嘅玩家應該係有主場地利優勢，雖然香城警察號稱世界第一，但係拳頭在近官府在遠，下面保命3招玩家必學而且容易學，所需工具玩家應該好清楚位置。<br />\n<br />\n示現流<br />\n<br />\n它的特色是強調由上方斜砍的大袈裟斬，希望在第一擊就把敵人砍殺。在攻擊時會發出很大的喊叫聲也是他的特色。當賊人半夜爆門入屋，巨大喊叫聲會招來其他人增援幫手，擊退賊人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3OIvwH9naT4&amp;t=363s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3OIvwH9naT4%26t%3D363s&d=W4F44tB2NhBwWjndCc5Bw0bB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=aca684e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3OIvwH9naT4&amp;t=363s</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n袈裟斬<br />\n<br />\n威力大，一擊必殺，配合燕返威力更強<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EV8ph5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEV8ph5d.jpg&h=27fbb8b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H9F_Iy4vAnw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DH9F_Iy4vAnw&d=W4F44tB2NhBwWjndCc5Bw0bB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=79a41c29\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H9F_Iy4vAnw</a><br />\n<br />\n羅馬式刺穿術<br />\n<br />\n實戰證實，刺穿比斬擊更有效更有傷害性，對賊人威力更大。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jnoiTX0xZ0Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjnoiTX0xZ0Y&d=W4F44tB2NhBwWjndCc5Bw0bB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=816bf7e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jnoiTX0xZ0Y</a><br />\n<br />\n當然，情況容許下，最好都係報官府等香城警察攪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea5b4d7e525d62dc8c37dc5685915cbdd004326e","tid":1915300,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T06:27:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6bd9e1fdf4c2b90d43f200c946c0d56fefa9b32","tid":1915300,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T06:28:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"084113c99bdca79724001a3938db167d4e4c1ef4","tid":1915300,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T06:28:46.000Z","msg":"借位 大家幫手推一推<br />\n［行動post入黎推一推］ 明天1930將軍澳*準時到*<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1914250\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1914250</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"af12ae62ef8fa51c8d49ce25adf11f0edfb76af9","tid":1915300,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T06:29:08.000Z","msg":"一個夠本，2個夠利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}